          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1595254323565-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the<strong> chopped parsley </strong>and<strong> capers</strong> with the <strong>white wine vinegar</strong>, <strong>Dijon mustard </strong>and 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and mix thoroughly – this is your <strong>salsa verde</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
