      "instruction": "<p>Deseed the<strong> pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</strong> </span>(scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced pepper</strong> to a separate baking tray and set aside</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
